Wanna look tall in a saree? Here are some quick and easy tips to keep in mind 🙌🏻👯‍♀️

💕 Avoid half and half shading or large borders 
💕 Go for smaller prints 
💕 Opt for vertical designs
💕 Match your saree and blouse colour/shade
💕 Go for a flowy playable fabric 
💕 Avoid low waist draping 

Let me know what do you want me to share in my next saree series ✨
